---
title: Curried Spinach and Paneer with Fragrant Cilantro Basmati
description: Tonight, we're bringing you a lighter version of the traditional saag paneer curry which pairs delicious Indian cottage cheese with spinach and spices. We've added fresh tomatoes and aromatic shallots for a flavour-packed veggie wonder!
